comments: Rondo (LAL) makes contact to Brogdon's (MIL) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Ilyasova (MIL) cleanly deflects the ball away from James (LAL) as he defends the inbound pass.
Ingram (LAL) legally contests Brogdon's (MIL) jump shot attempt.
Kuzma (LAL) engages with Antetokounmpo (MIL) but does not affect his ability to secure the rebound.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes marginal contact with Rondo (LAL) as the defenders switch after the pick.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) rolls to the rim and makes marginal contact with Caldwell-Pope (LAL) as he attempts to establish post position.
RAR shows Caldwell-Pope (LAL) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Antetokounmpo (MIL) that does not affect his SQBR.
[Observable in enhanced video] Antetokounmpo (MIL) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
LAR shows Antetokounmpo (MIL) leaves his feet to pass and he releases the ball before his foot returns to the floor.
Kuzma (LAL) is already in Ilyasova's (MIL) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) places his hand momentarily on Kuzma's (LAL) hip before immediately correcting.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) commits a take foul on Middleton (MIL).
LAR and MOB show Ilyasova (MIL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends James' (LAL) shot near the rim.
Ingram (LAL) commits a take foul on Middleton (MIL).
